subtitle: Tik Tok மீதான தடையை உச்ச நீதிமன்றம் நீக்கியதா ? - YouTurn - Fake News Checker Online.

vclaim: Supreme Court asks Madras High Court to decide on a plea against ban order on video app TikTok on April 24. A Bench of Chief Justice Ranjan Gogoi says “if the plea is not decided by then, the order by the High Court imposing ban on the App would be vacated.” pic.twitter.com/3DwMURAM2n
